# Project Demo

This folder contains the demonstration of the **Machine Learning-based Fabric Defect Detection System**.

The demo showcases:

* User interface of the application
* Image upload process
* Fabric defect detection workflow
* Model prediction results
* Overall system functionality

The project is designed to provide an automated, cost-effective, and high-accuracy solution for fabric quality inspection using Machine Learning techniques.

